      to <code><?=htmlspecialchars($cfg['HERMES_HOME_PATH'])?></code>.<br>
      Services restarted with the new path. Verify everything works, then click Clean Up.
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:10px;">
      <button class="hermes-btn" id="hermes-cleanup-migration" style="background:#e74c3c;border-color:#c0392b">Clean Up Old Directory</button>
    </div>
